quran[35]{c,v,t}:
  26,70,"When He said to his father and his nation: \"What (do) you worship"
  26,71,"They said: \"We worship idols/statues so we continue/remain to it devoting/dedicating"
  26,72,"He said: \"Do they hear/listen to you when/if you call"
  26,73,Or they benefit you or they harm
  26,74,"They said: \"But we found our fathers as/like that they make/do"
  26,75,"He said: \"Did you see/understand what you were worshipping"
  26,76,You and your fathers/forefathers the eldest/old/ancient
  26,77,So they truly are an enemy to me except the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord
  26,78,"Who created me, so He guides me"
  26,79,And who He feeds me and He gives me drink
  26,80,"And if I became sick/diseased, so He cures/heals me"
  26,81,"And who makes me die, then revives/makes me alive"
  26,82,And who I wish/hope/covet that He forgives for me my sin/wrong (on) the Judgment`s Day/Resurrection260Day
  26,83,"My Lord, grant/present for me judgment/rule and make me catch up/join with the correct/righteous"
  26,84,And make/put for me (a) truth`s tongue/speech in the ends/lasts/others
  26,85,And make/put me from the blessing`s/comfort and eases` treed garden`s/paradise`s heirs
  26,86,"And forgive to my father, that he truly was from the misguided"
  26,87,And do not shame/disgrace me (on) a day/time they are being resurrected/revived
  26,88,A day/time property/possession and nor sons/sons and daughters do not benefit
  26,89,Except who came (to) God with a sound/safe (clear) heart/mind
  26,90,And paradise was advanced/brought near to the fearing and obeying
  26,91,And the Hell/place of intense heat was made to emerge for the misguided/lured
  26,92,"And (it) was said to them: \"Where (is) what you were worshipping"
  26,93,From other than God? Do they give you victory/aid or they become victorious
  26,94,"So they were thrown down in it, they and the enticing"
  26,95,And Satan`s soldiers/warriors all/all together
  26,96,They said and (while) they are in it disputing/arguing
  26,97,"By God, that truly we were in clear/evident misguidance"
  26,98,When/if we make you equal with the creations all together`s/(universes`) Lord
  26,99,And none except the criminals/sinners misguided us
  26,100,So (there are) none for us from mediators
  26,101,And nor a concerned friend
  26,102,And if that (E) (there were) for us a return/repetition so we be/become from the believers
  26,103,"That truly in that (is) an evidence/sign (E) , and most of them were not believing"
  26,104,"And that truly your Lord, He is (E) the glorious/mighty , the merciful"